---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Support a Cause | Living Branch Development" description="Support Living Branch Development with a one-time or monthly gift that helps children, families, and communities access education, health care, and livelihood support.">
  <section class="border-b border-(--border) bg-white">
    <div class="container-page grid gap-10 py-14 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center lg:gap-14 lg:py-18">
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-(--muted)">
          Let&rsquo;s help together
        </p>
        <h1 class="mt-3 font-heading text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-(--fg) sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
          MAKE A DONATION
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-(--muted) sm:text-base">
          Your support fuels education, health care, and livelihood programmes that protect dignity and open real pathways for children, families, and communities.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-7 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a
            href="/donate/bank-details"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-linear-to-r from-orange-500 to-red-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition hover:from-orange-600 hover:to-red-600 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-orange-300/60"
          >
            View bank details
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute right-4 top-10 hidden h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-orange-200/60 md:block" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-lg">
          <!-- Illustration (inline SVG) -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 760 420" class="h-auto w-full" aria-hidden="true">
            <!-- Hand -->
            <path d="M360 305c70-30 140-44 220-42 38 1 67 19 78 48 9 24-1 49-24 62-30 17-79 16-132 13-62-4-125-10-182 12-26 10-56-5-65-30-8-22 2-50 25-63 24-14 54-14 80 0Z" fill="#F2B39B"/>
            <!-- Orange circle -->
            <circle cx="410" cy="240" r="120" fill="#F09A86" opacity="0.9"/>

            <!-- Phone -->
            <g transform="translate(420 120) rotate(12)">
              <rect x="0" y="0" rx="26" ry="26" width="210" height="300" fill="#2B2144"/>
              <rect x="16" y="24" rx="16" ry="16" width="178" height="246" fill="#FFFFFF"/>
              <rect x="85" y="282" rx="8" ry="8" width="40" height="8" fill="#463667" opacity="0.8"/>
            </g>

            <!-- Donation box -->
            <g transform="translate(470 170)">
              <path d="M40 40 110 20 190 50 120 70Z" fill="#2D6A4F" opacity="0.95"/>
              <path d="M40 40v92l80 28 70-28V50l-70 20Z" fill="#3B8A63"/>
              <path d="M120 70v90l70-28V50Z" fill="#2F7A57"/>
              <path d="M58 82h120" stroke="#204D3A" stroke-width="6" opacity="0.35"/>
              <path d="M88 96h60" stroke="#204D3A" stroke-width="6" opacity="0.25"/>
            </g>

            <!-- Coins -->
            <g transform="translate(520 70)">
              <g transform="translate(0 0)">
                <ellipse cx="34" cy="34" rx="28" ry="18" fill="#F6D06F"/>
                <ellipse cx="34" cy="32" rx="28" ry="18" fill="#F4C85E"/>
                <path d="M20 32h28" stroke="#E3A93D" stroke-width="4" opacity="0.8"/>
              </g>
              <g transform="translate(70 18)">
                <ellipse cx="34" cy="34" rx="28" ry="18" fill="#F6D06F"/>
                <ellipse cx="34" cy="32" rx="28" ry="18" fill="#F4C85E"/>
                <path d="M20 32h28" stroke="#E3A93D" stroke-width="4" opacity="0.8"/>
              </g>
              <g transform="translate(28 78)">
                <ellipse cx="34" cy="34" rx="28" ry="18" fill="#F6D06F"/>
                <ellipse cx="34" cy="32" rx="28" ry="18" fill="#F4C85E"/>
                <path d="M20 32h28" stroke="#E3A93D" stroke-width="4" opacity="0.8"/>
              </g>
              <!-- Hearts -->
              <path d="M12 72c0-10 14-12 18-2 4-10 18-8 18 2 0 12-18 20-18 20S12 84 12 72Z" fill="#F59CB5" opacity="0.9"/>
              <path d="M150 64c0-9 12-11 16-2 4-9 16-7 16 2 0 10-16 17-16 17s-16-7-16-17Z" fill="#F59CB5" opacity="0.9"/>
            </g>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container-page py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.2fr)_minmax(0,0.9fr)] md:items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[var(--muted)]">Why your gift matters</p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 font-heading text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--fg)] sm:text-3xl">
          From one act of kindness to long-term change.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--muted)] sm:text-base">
          When you give to Living Branch Development, you are investing in children who stay in school, families
          who can access timely health care, and young people who gain the skills to support themselves and
          others.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--muted)] sm:text-base">
          Our team works with local partners to ensure that every rupee is used with care, transparency, and
          accountability.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-white/90 p-4 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[var(--muted)]">
            Education
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-navy)_85%,black)]">
            2.4K+
          </p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-[var(--muted)]">
            children supported with learning, nutrition, and safe spaces.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-white/90 p-4 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[var(--muted)]">
            Health
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-cyan)_85%,black)]">
            3K+
          </p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-[var(--muted)]">
            families reached through health check-ups, referrals, and awareness.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-white/90 p-4 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[var(--muted)]">
            Livelihoods
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-orange)_85%,black)]">
            800+
          </p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-[var(--muted)]">
            youth and caregivers trained with employable skills.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-(--border) bg-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-orange)_6%,white)]">
    <div class="container-page py-12 sm:py-16">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-(--muted)">Donation flow</p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 font-heading text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-(--fg) sm:text-3xl">
          Simple to give. Clear to track. Real to feel.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-(--muted) sm:text-base">
          We keep the giving process straightforward while sharing how support reaches families—so you can give
          with confidence.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
        <article class="rounded-3xl border border-(--border) bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="inline-flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-orange)_18%,white)] text-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-orange)_85%,black)] ring-1 ring-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-orange)_28%,white)]" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M12 2v4" />
                <path d="M7 6h10" />
                <path d="M6 10h12" />
                <path d="M7 14h10" />
                <path d="M9 18h6" />
                <path d="M12 22v-4" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-(--muted)">Step 1</p>
              <h3 class="mt-2 font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-(--fg)">Choose bank transfer</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-(--muted)">
                Open the bank details and copy what you need—account title and IBAN—right from your phone.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-3xl border border-(--border) bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="inline-flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-orange)_18%,white)] text-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-orange)_85%,black)] ring-1 ring-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-orange)_28%,white)]" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M7 7h10" />
                <path d="M7 11h10" />
                <path d="M7 15h6" />
                <path d="M5 3h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2Z" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-(--muted)">Step 2</p>
              <h3 class="mt-2 font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-(--fg)">Send the transfer</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-(--muted)">
                Use your banking app to transfer any amount. Keep the receipt/reference for your records.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-3xl border border-(--border) bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="inline-flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-orange)_18%,white)] text-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-orange)_85%,black)] ring-1 ring-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-orange)_28%,white)]" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M12 21s-7-4.5-7-11a4 4 0 0 1 7-2 4 4 0 0 1 7 2c0 6.5-7 11-7 11Z" />
                <path d="M9.6 12.3 11 13.7 14.6 10" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-(--muted)">Step 3</p>
              <h3 class="mt-2 font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-(--fg)">We put it to work</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-(--muted)">
                Your support is applied to programme needs—education, health, livelihood support, and emergency response.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr] lg:items-start">
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-(--border) bg-white p-6 shadow-sm sm:p-8">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-(--muted)">Transparency</p>
              <h3 class="mt-2 font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-(--fg)">How support reaches families</h3>
            </div>
            <span class="inline-flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-orange)_14%,white)] text-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-orange)_85%,black)] ring-1 ring-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-orange)_25%,white)]" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M12 2l8 4v6c0 5-3 9-8 10-5-1-8-5-8-10V6l8-4Z" />
                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" />
              </svg>
            </span>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-(--border) bg-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-orange)_6%,white)] p-4">
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-(--muted)">Programmes</p>
              <p class="mt-2 font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-navy)_85%,black)]">85%</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-xs leading-relaxed text-(--muted)">Direct delivery: supplies, training, support sessions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-(--border) bg-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-orange)_6%,white)] p-4">
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-(--muted)">Operations</p>
              <p class="mt-2 font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-navy)_85%,black)]">10%</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-xs leading-relaxed text-(--muted)">Field coordination, transport, and essential admin.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-(--border) bg-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-orange)_6%,white)] p-4">
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-(--muted)">Reporting</p>
              <p class="mt-2 font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-navy)_85%,black)]">5%</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-xs leading-relaxed text-(--muted)">Monitoring, documentation, and impact updates.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="mt-5 text-xs text-(--muted)">
            These percentages are a simple, donor-friendly breakdown and can be updated with audited figures anytime.
          </p>
        </div>

        <aside class="rounded-3xl border border-(--border) bg-white p-6 shadow-sm sm:p-8">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-(--muted)">Next step</p>
          <h3 class="mt-2 font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-(--fg)">Ready to donate?</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-(--muted)">
            Open the bank transfer details, copy the IBAN, and send your gift in minutes.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-5 grid gap-3">
            <a
              href="/donate/bank-details"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-linear-to-r from-orange-500 to-red-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition hover:from-orange-600 hover:to-red-600 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-orange-300/60"
            >
              View bank details
            </a>
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-(--border) bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-(--fg) transition hover:border-(--brand-navy)"
            >
              Ask a question
            </a>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

